{\displaystyle a_{ij}} & \longleftarrow & {\displaystyle \frac{\left({x_{i}+y_{1}}\right)-\left({x_{i}+y_{j}}\right)}{\left({x_{i}+y_{j}}\right)\left({x_{i}+y_{1}}\right)}}\\
