\end_inset

 we define the powers of 
\begin_inset Formula $A$
\end_inset

 by
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{eqnarray*}
A^{0} & = & I_{n},\\
A^{k} & = & \underbrace{A\star A\star\cdot\cdot\cdot\star A}_{k-\textrm{times}},\quad\textrm{for }k\in\mathbf{N}.
