\end_inset

.
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\cdot\,:\, R\times R^{n,m}\longrightarrow R^{n,m},\quad\left(\lambda,\, A\right)\longmapsto\lambda\cdot A=\left[\lambda a_{ij}\right].
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Note that 
\begin_inset Formula $0\cdot A=0_{n,m}$
\end_inset

 and 
\begin_inset Formula $1\cdot A=A$
\end_inset

.
