\emph on
quotient module
\emph default
 
\begin_inset Formula $M/S$
\end_inset

 is the quotient group 
\begin_inset Formula $M/S$
\end_inset

 with scalar multiplication defined by 
\begin_inset Formula $\lambda\left(x+S\right)=\lambda x+S$
\end_inset

 for all 
\begin_inset Formula $\lambda\in R$
