\begin_inset Formula $T\,\colon\, V\longrightarrow V$
\end_inset

 be a linear transformation of a vector space 
\begin_inset Formula $V$
\end_inset

.
 A subspace 
\begin_inset Formula $U\subset V$
\end_inset

 is called a 
