\]

\end_inset

where 
\begin_inset Formula $A$
\end_inset

 is an 
\begin_inset Formula $m\times m$
\end_inset

 matrix representing the restriction transformation 
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
T\big|_{U}\,\colon\, U\longrightarrow U
\]

\end_inset

 relative to the basis 
\begin_inset Formula $v_{1},\ldots,v_{m}$
\end_inset

.
\end_layout

